text: Mitchell Evan Haniger (born December 23, 1990) is an American professional baseball outfielder for the San Francisco Giants of Major League Baseball (MLB). He used to play for the Arizona Diamondbacks and Seattle Mariners of the MLB. He was born in Mountain View, California.
